<BaseLayout title="HiEN">
  <section class="surface surface--glow hero">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <div class="eyebrow">Xin chào !!!</div>
        <h1>I’m HiEN</h1>
        <p class="prose">
          I’m an independent engineer and data scientist focused on environmental,
          climate, earth observation, and ecological data challenges. I like
          building practical, open-source tools that bridge software engineering,
          analytics, and geospatial science to push environmental intelligence
          forward.
        </p>
        <p class="prose">
          My projects usually translate messy datasets into decision-ready
          systems—remote sensing workflows, conservation monitoring platforms,
          climate-risk dashboards, or resilient urban analytics. Whatever the
          form factor, the goal stays the same: useful software for
          environmental insight and action.
        </p>
        <p class="prose">
          You can explore my code on <a
            href="https://github.com/enguy-hub"
            target="_blank">GitHub</a
          >, review my research trail on
          <a
            href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Hien-Nguyen-153"
            target="_blank">ResearchGate</a
          >, and connect professionally on
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/hien-nguyen--/" target="_blank"
            >LinkedIn</a
          >. I’m always up for conversations about climate tech, remote sensing,
          and open science.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="cta-button" href="/projects">
            Explore Projects
            <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
          </a>
          <a class="ghost-button" href="/blogs"> Latest Blogs </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
